<br>
<br>
<br>
No!<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
There is no place in a world of perfection, a world of Light for the mad.  If they can be cast amongst the enemy to fight with or weaken them, excellent!  If not, cut them down where they stand.  For their own good, and the good of all Norrath.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
To those questioning 'who can say what is good or evil', I say wake up!  If you cannot determine for yourselves, then I will do so for you.  Judge, or be judged.  The swords of the righteous will not be stayed by empty words.  Act or be acted upon.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Of those born in the Dark who would walk in the Light:  it may be possible to achieve redemption.  Is it not like a Mother to forgive?  However, until the day Neriak is a smoldering ruin, the priests of hatred and the great houses are slaughtered to the last soul, and the memory of what a Teir'Dal should be is annihilated, can a child of Innoruuk hope to escape him?  So it is for all who would escape the Evil they are born into.  The best such a one can hope for is to die for the Light and be born anew as a child of it.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
There is a perfection in both Light and Darkness, good and evil.  Hence the conflict between the two.  The battle rages on.  Those who walk the middle path are an abomination to both, for they weaken both.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Fear not you of the madness, walking in the shadows.  The enemy dwells in the darkness of hatred, pain, fear, death and decay.  You will stand against them or you will fall with them.  It is your choice and you will be held accountable for it.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Soon the Light will shine in the darkest of places, and the blood of those who dwell therein shall be the food of the new Life which will grow there.  A new day is upon the world, a day which will last forever!  Perfect order in eternal light is what shall come to pass; nothing less will suffice.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Iosefis Iceheart:<br>
<br>
Arbiter of Rectitude,<br>
Office of Tunare Triumphant. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23>Hero Heart Tavern</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.240<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

